Asia, Middle East and North Africa
Either independently  or in conjunction with third parties, AMENA  makes, markets, distributes and sells a
number of leading snack food brands including Cheetos, Chipsy , Doritos, Kurkure and Lay’s, as well as many
Quaker branded cereals and snacks, through consolidated businesses, as well as through noncontrolled
affiliates. AMENA  also makes, market s, distributes and sells beverage conce ntrates, fountain syrups and
