Refranchising in Jordan
In 2017, we refranchised our beverage business in Jordan by selling a controlling interest in our Jordan
bottling operations to form a joint venture, where we now have an equity metho d investment. We recorded a
pre-tax gain of $140 million  ($107 million  after-tax or $0.07  per share) in selling, general and administrative
expenses in our AMENA  segment as a result of this transaction.
